    "As shown in Fig. 4, the level-based performances were given using AUC value in predicting the testing data, and the performances of AnnoPRO, DeepGOPlus, NetGO3, and PFmulDL were shown by light red, light green, orange, and light blue, respectively (also provided in Supplementary Table S1).",
